quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  6,111,"“۞ Ndipo ngati tikadawatumizira angelo (kuti adzaikire umboni za uneneri wako), ndipo akufa nkuwayankhula, (naonso nkuvomereza kuti izi nzoona; kuonjezera apo) nkuwasonkhanitsira chinthu chilichonse pamaso pawo, sakadakhulupirira pokhapokha Allah akadafuna koma ambiri a iwo sazindikira"
  6,112,"“Ndipo nchomwechi tidamuikira adani mneneri aliyense (omwe) ndi asatana a mu anthu ndi asatana a m’ziwanda, (omwe) amadziwitsana wina ndi mnzake mawu okometsa ncholinga chonyenga. Ndipo Mbuye wako akadafuna, sakadatha kuchita zimenezi choncho asiye ndi zimene akupeka"
  6,113,"“Ndi kuti ipendekere ku mawu amenewo mitima ya anthu osakhulupirira tsiku la chimaliziro, ndi kuyanjana nawo (mawuo) ndikutinso apeze (machimo) omwe amawapeza"
  6,114,"“(Nena:) “Kodi ndifune woweruza wina kusiya Allah, pomwe Iye ndi Yemwe adavumbulutsa buku kwa inu lofotokoza chilichonse?” Ndipo omwe tidawapatsa buku akudziwa kuti (Qur’an) yavumbulutsidwa ndi Mbuye wako mwachoonadi. Choncho, usakhale mwa okaikira"
  6,115,"“Ndipo mawu a Mbuye wako akwanira moona ndi mwachilungamo. Palibe amene angathe kusintha mawu Ake. Iye Ngwakumva, Ngodziwa"
  6,116,"“Ngati umvera ambiri amene ali pa dziko lapansi, akusokeretsa pa njira ya Allah. Satsatira koma zakungoganizira. Ndipo sali chilichonse koma akungonama"
  6,117,"“Ndithu Mbuye wako ndi Yemwe akudziwa bwino amene asokera ku njira Yake, ndiponso Iye akudziwa bwino za oongoka"
  6,118,"“Choncho, idyani (nyama) zomwe dzina la Allah latchulidwapo (pozizinga osati zofa zokha), ngati inu mukhulupiriradi Ayah (zizindikiro) Zake"
  6,119,"“Mungasiirenji kudya (nyama) imene poizinga dzina la Allah latchulidwapo, pomwe wakufotokozerani momveka chomwe wachiletsa kwa inu, kupatula (mukadya choletsedwacho) mosimidwa ndi kukakamizidwa (chifukwa cha njala)? Koma ndithu ambiri akusokeretsa (ena) mwa zifuniro zawo popanda kudziwa. Ndithu Mbuye wako ndi Yemwe akudziwa bwino za olumpha malire"
  6,120,“Siyani machimo oonekera ndi obisika. Ndithu amene achita machimo adzalipidwa chifukwa cha zomwe adali kuchita (zoipa)
  6,121,"“Ndipo musadye (nyama) imene yazingidwa popanda kutchula dzina la Allah. Kutero ndikuchimwa. Ndithudi, asatana amanong’onezera abwenzi awo kuti akangane ndi inu (m’zinthu zonga zimenezi). Ngati muwamvera, ndiye kuti mukhala opembedza mafano"